:0,"score":35,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T09:52:15.000Z","msg":"智障並非減刑理由都講得出"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T10:02:47.000Z","msg":"智陣並非減刑理由，但黑警因佔中壓力大犯罪就係減刑理由<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73f21582a538271f2826074aba108697983a666b","tid":2270941,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07265126b74a5310e3d791253bab860ecbafb436","tid":2270941,"uid":230104,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T09:52:15.000Z","msg":"智障並非減刑理由都講得出"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T10:02:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caf9a0436935a4e92d1e57d0e61ea2120e422801","tid":2270941,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T10:03:41.000Z","msg":"赤納粹甲級戰犯張潔宜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62b1d45638241047dd4bdef0e881fe4845f9953f","tid":2270941,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T10:12:56.000Z","msg":"有委任證可獲減刑？"},{"pid":"8d1d0da3d3e0c9170bb42cb5bdf98ff40e25c837","tid":2270941,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T10:17:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b313c5872164bc3e3a8f001d1456cf7533b9757","tid":2270941,"uid":230104,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T10:22:08.000Z","msg":"發仔及後撐傘離開法庭，被問到心情時表示「有諗過入嘅其實」。邵透露發仔本已有最壞打算，但上訴得直，「（發仔）個心安樂咗好多」。邵坦言裁決最有意義的，是推翻原審裁判官指智障並非減刑理由的說法，強調「弱智係一個求情理由」，認為對往後案件有重要影響。邵又稱將與發仔午膳，笑謂：「佢話想食茶餐廳，我依家唔知邊度搵茶餐廳畀佢。」"},{"pid":"b63abdffcb7033f981309489c21cc92ffcc7d0d3","tid":2270941,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1bf61388fa17ab614a566db97b80b63667022c2","tid":2270941,"uid":13503,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T09:53:33.000Z","msg":"似係個法官先係智障<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T10:23:49.000Z","msg":"智障非誤判理由就真<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1ae4d7ba27e079cfb99587d596848b20eb3a2e3","tid":2270941,"uid":230104,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T10:23:53.000Z","msg":"大律師黃瑞紅今陳詞時質疑，原審裁判官不考慮智障作為求情理由，又沒考慮智障問題加重被告服刑的負擔，皆屬犯錯。另外，黃亦質疑裁判官以12個月作量刑起點，明顯過高。黃又補充，上訴人已還柙4個半月，還柙期間曾受欺凌要調倉，強調上訴人無法控制自身的缺陷，導致他與囚友相處苦難重重。"},{"pid":"16a98ae3cb363e473336bad4a20401e10d129ff6","tid":2270941,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T11:21:47.000Z","msg":"撥亂反正"},{"pid":"3963d14e975d495dcdc8e51caf891887281bbcb0","tid":2270941,"uid":14941,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T11:23:01.000Z","msg":"智障放火魔可以無罪！明白晒！"},{"pid":"8bb5cdd37c0f9721239fac076105f7d4f5104253","tid":2270941,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3963d14e975d495dcdc8e51caf891887281bbcb0","tid":2270941,"uid":14941,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T11:23:01.000Z","msg":"智障放火魔可以無罪！明白晒！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T11:24:20.000Z","msg":"你老母可以生到你，明白晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99c8b775594aa896365323ca9c2be46751da3785","tid":2270941,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T11:26:25.000Z","msg":"判詞<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gijvZRA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgijvZRA.png&h=8b02e842&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w0z0CDh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw0z0CDh.png&h=b3123f43&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nBpG6wF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna